* D shook himself and gave a little snort towards Vlad's direction before he 
turned and began to follow Fenox, moving up so that his head was right 
beside her shoulder.
He bumped his cheek against it.*

" Where now?"

* He wanted to know where they were going, and he wouldn't mind hearing 
about it in detail. He was still learning and he wanted to know all he could 
about this new world now.*
